high_descs: Walk over to the door, then turn right and walk up to the cabinet.
Pick up the blue bottle off of the top of the cabinet.
Turn right and walk over to the sink, then turn right and walk up to the wall, turn right again to face the toilet.
Put the blue bottle on top of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk over to the left side of the tub.
Pick up the blue bottle off of the tub.
Walk back over to the toilet.
Put the blue bottle on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two blue bottles to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Walk forward and turn to face the upright, two-drawer table.
Pick up the bottle of soap with the green top.
Turn right and keep turning right until you see the toilet and walk over to it.
Place the bottle of soap on top of the toilet tank, to the front left of the empty toilet paper roll.
Turn right and then turn right again then walk over to tub and turn left to the get to the corner of the tub.
Pick up the green-topped soap bottle on the tub.
Turn left then right and walk over to the toilet and stop.
Put this soap bottle behind the existing soap bottle on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of soap on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Go to the counter next to the blue bin
Pick up the perfume bottle
Go to the toilet
Put the perfume bottle on top of the toilet
Go to the tub
Pick up the perfume bottle on top of the tub
Go to the toilet
Put the perfume bottle on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Move two perfume bottles to the top of a toilet
